{"tid":187732,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"單親父親挨餓讓女兒食炸雞😭","createTime":"2017-04-05T07:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T03:47:48.000Z","uid":12628,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d1418449e9784151fb16b7bd9289f87c0f97c1","tid":187732,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"男人說不出的苦與悲。<br />\n雖然貼呢篇野比連登小學睇有啲晒氣，不過人間有情，唔係人人都咁幸福嘅，希望大家愛錫下父母家人<br />\n<br />\n單親父親挨餓讓女兒食炸雞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbAyYSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbAyYSb.jpg&h=fdb7ff4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓有網民早前在社交網站分享三父女到快餐店的照片，相中兩位小女孩在吃炸雞，身旁的爸爸就看著女兒捱餓，照片廣泛流傳後，快餐店招呼他們一起吃炸雞，還帶他們到超市買日用品，令他落下男兒淚。<br />\n　　網友撒拉葉（Jhunnel Sarajan）早前在facebook上載照片，單親爸爸阿拉布韋波（Ryan Arabuebo）帶著兩個女兒到Jollibee吃炸雞，但他只在一旁觀看捱餓讓女兒享受炸雞，讓不少網友感動，多國傳媒都有報道事件。"},{"pid":"d6b92fb4b4929ca7e74baf269c040f9e1951355a","tid":187732,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0abac79191d39516ceac928d329fc7786b1edb","tid":187732,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7124f16ce6cc0b9ef95f44f61f741dc0be873dbb","tid":187732,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:12:19.000Z","msg":"就算窮但有個咁錫自己嘅老豆已經好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532ece7430cccc6000610377d2566d3c750351d5","tid":187732,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"細個時試過父母唔食，讓比自己食晒成個餐嘅朋友應該明果種感動"},{"pid":"3825cc027ff107ec10ae180f957912729dfb12ee","tid":187732,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚窮仆野不用套？<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線公司"},{"pid":"2961051b45d509a8cf8b7828de942c8705a